# 5) Role-Based Prompting

**Definition:** Assign a **persona/expert role** and constraints.

**Finance (as CFA PM):**
â€œAs a **CFA-charterholder PM**, write a 1-page **risk memo** on overweighting utilities during tightening. Include macro view, valuation comps, downside.â€

**Sales (as VP Sales Ops):**
â€œAs **VP Sales Ops**, create a **QBR template** (pipeline, win/loss, enablement, top 5 risks).â€

**IT (as SRE):**
â€œAs an **SRE**, propose **error budget policies** for a 99.9% SLA API.â€

**Risk & Compliance (as CISO):**
â€œAs **CISO**, draft a **third-party breach response** playbook (72-hour notice, regulators, customers).â€

**HR (as Comp & Ben Lead):**
â€œAs **Comp Lead**, design a **bonus plan** for SDRs (quota credit, accelerators, caps).â€

**Legal (as Privacy Counsel):**
â€œAs **Privacy Counsel**, write a **DPIA outline** for a new biometric login feature.â€

