# 6) Iterative (Refinement) Prompting

**Definition:** Produce a draft, then **tighten** via targeted follow-ups.

**Finance:**

1. â€œDraft a **macro note** on a soft-landing scenario.â€
2. â€œNow **add charts** we should include and write captions.â€
3. â€œCondense into a **200-word client note** with 3 bullets.â€

**Sales:**

1. â€œWrite a **case study** for a 15% churn reduction.â€
2. â€œRefine with **ROI calc** and timeline.â€
3. â€œCreate a **1-slide summary**.â€

**IT:**

1. â€œPropose a **zero-trust** rollout.â€
2. â€œRefine with **Okta/Entra** specifics.â€
3. â€œAdd a **90-day roadmap**.â€

**Risk & Compliance:**

1. â€œDraft **KYB/KYC** SOP.â€
2. â€œTighten with **PEP/sanctions** specifics.â€
3. â€œAdd **audit evidence** list.â€

**HR:**

1. â€œCreate a **performance review rubric**.â€
2. â€œRefine with **behavioral examples**.â€
3. â€œAdd **bias-mitigation** guidance.â€

**Legal:**

1. â€œWrite a **standard DPA** summary.â€
2. â€œTailor to **sub-processors** in US/EU.â€
3. â€œAdd a **negotiation fallback**.â€

